Package com.github.cwilper.fcrepo.store.util.filters.ds

Built-in Filter<Datastream> implementations.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CanonicalizeManagedXML Canonicalizes (using C14N11 rules) managed xml.
CheckFixity Computes the fixity (size and/or digest) and compares it to the stored values, reporting on any differences.
IfControlGroupMatches Accepts datastreams whose control group matches a given IdSpec.
IfIdMatches Accepts datastreams whose ids match a given IdSpec.
InlineToManagedXML Converts inline XML to managed content (which will be canonicalized using C14N11 rules).
ListDatastreams Lists each datastream.
MultiVersionFilter A datastream filter that accepts all versions, but may examine or change any of them.
RemoveOldVersions Drops all versions of each datastream except the most recent.
SetFixity Sets the fixity (size and digest) where undefined, or forcibly overwrites the previously stored fixity values.
